Date: Tue, 17 Feb 2026 08:39:19 -0600
Subject: [PATCH 15/42] Add mouse events and URL change notifications

A click set sail from Swift's domain,
Through XPC seas to Chromium's brain.
ForwardMouseEvent caught the call,
While DidFinishNavigation told all:
"The URL has changed!" it would explain.

Co-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.6 <noreply@anthropic.com>
